category: Games
requires: libintl8 libSDL1.2_0 libSDL_mixer1.2_0
sdesc: "SDL Tetris game"
ldesc: "LTris as a tetris clone: differently shaped blocks are falling 
down the rectangular playing field and can be moved sideways or rotated 
by 90 degree units with the aim of building lines without gaps which 
then disappear (causing any block above the deleted line to fall down)."
